  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/d73f8dc768f7d0a30c65fe1ca238ed83.avif?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=215 /></span><br><br>ArcticBoy Story - This is an interactive movie with first-person gameplay elements based on the acclaimed history of the Arctic Kokold. Young Alexei living on the distant island of Spitsbergen, in search of fun, finds the post of a lonely girl living in the city of Barentsburg. She really wants rolls. Brought up to help single girls, Alexey decides to immediately deliver those same rolls and charm her with his kindness, but not everything goes as Alexei wants.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/3a584812eb4f42f122574a337d6d91b5.webp?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=26 /></span><br><br>-Beautiful graphics<br>-Cinematic cutscenes<br>-Riding a snowmobile<br>-Search for sticks<br>-Sound by professional actors<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/756338e156fcffbc7bb6d8625898775a.avif?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=257 /></span><br><br>Drive your snowmobile to the distant city of Barentsburg. Make your way through blizzards and snow. Don't let the bear ruin the rolls and save Anya from hunger.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/3a584812eb4f42f122574a337d6d91b5.webp?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=26 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/5fc71d5975528ba2add0d66052528f32.poster.avif?t=1622905174\" width=636 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/5fc71d5975528ba2add0d66052528f32.webm?t=1622905174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/5fc71d5975528ba2add0d66052528f32.mp4?t=1622905174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/36f377336b2fb7186230b3e77d2e828b.avif?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=67 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/11a3dbf269a908e9458254c2c61086f2.avif?t=1622905174\" width=636 height=256 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/d73f8dc768f7d0a30c65fe1ca238ed83.avif?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=215 /></span><br><br>ArcticBoy Story - This is an interactive movie with first-person gameplay elements based on the acclaimed history of the Arctic Kokold. Young Alexei living on the distant island of Spitsbergen, in search of fun, finds the post of a lonely girl living in the city of Barentsburg. She really wants rolls. Brought up to help single girls, Alexey decides to immediately deliver those same rolls and charm her with his kindness, but not everything goes as Alexei wants.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/3a584812eb4f42f122574a337d6d91b5.webp?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=26 /></span><br><br>-Beautiful graphics<br>-Cinematic cutscenes<br>-Riding a snowmobile<br>-Search for sticks<br>-Sound by professional actors<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/756338e156fcffbc7bb6d8625898775a.avif?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=257 /></span><br><br>Drive your snowmobile to the distant city of Barentsburg. Make your way through blizzards and snow. Don't let the bear ruin the rolls and save Anya from hunger.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/3a584812eb4f42f122574a337d6d91b5.webp?t=1622905174\" width=637 height=26 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587970/extras/5fc71d5975528ba2add0d66052528f32.poster.avif?t=1622905174\" width=636 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com